# Remarks: Gather input from user about about many cookies they want to make, and give the user the output of how much sugar, butter, and flour they need.

cookies=int(input("How many cookies would you like? "))     #Input for cookies
sugar=(cookies/48)*1.5                                      #Calculate sugar in cups
butter=(cookies/48)*1                                       #Calculate butter in cups
flour=(cookies/48)*2.75                                     #Calculate flour in cups

#Print results
print("You need", sugar,"cups of sugar", butter,"cups of butter, and", flour, "cups of flour.")   
